---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Get in touch with the EoES organising team about speaking, sponsoring or volunteering for EoES 2027."
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="bg-year" aria-hidden="true">@</div>
  <span class="spark" style="top: 22%; left: 7%;"></span>
  <span class="spark sm" style="top: 70%; right: 12%;"></span>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow"><div class="chip chip--purple"><span class="dot"></span><span>Contact · EoES</span></div></div>
    <h1 class="display-1 hero-title" style="max-width: 14ch;">Say <span class="display-italic">hello.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Questions about attending, speaking, sponsoring or volunteering? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap: 48px;">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 22px;">— Get in touch —</div>
        <h2 class="display-3" style="margin-bottom: 28px;">How to reach us.</h2>

        <div class="stack-6">
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 18px; align-items: start;">
            <div class="card-icon yellow" style="margin: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 0h-14c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5v14c0 2.76 2.24 5 5 5h14c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5v-14c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.27c-.97 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.76s.78-1.76 1.75-1.76 1.75.79 1.75 1.76-.78 1.76-1.75 1.76zm13.5 12.27h-3v-5.6c0-3.37-4-3.11-4 0v5.6h-3v-11h3v1.77c1.4-2.59 7-2.78 7 2.47v6.76z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Follow on LinkedIn</h3>
              <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">Stay updated with speaker announcements, schedule news, and event updates — LinkedIn is where we post first.</p>
              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/eoes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--yellow); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px;">linkedin.com/company/eoes</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 18px; align-items: start;">
            <div class="card-icon pink" style="margin: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Email us</h3>
              <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">For general enquiries — sponsorship, speaking, partnerships, press.</p>
              <a href="mailto:info@eoepps.co.uk" style="color: var(--yellow); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px;">info@eoepps.co.uk</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 18px; align-items: start;">
            <div class="card-icon cyan" style="margin: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17.66 16.66L13.41 20.9a2 2 0 01-2.83 0l-4.24-4.24a8 8 0 1111.31 0zM15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px;">Find us in Norwich</h3>
              <p class="muted">Both days in central Norwich, 30 April – 1 May 2027. Specific venues announced soon — see <a href="/venue" style="color: var(--yellow);">venue info</a>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 48px 1fr; gap: 18px; align-items: start;">
            <div class="card-icon purple" style="margin: 0; width: 48px; height: 48px;">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.66 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.34-9-3-9m0 18c-1.66 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.34-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="h3" style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 6px;">NPPUG monthly meetups</h3>
              <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">EoES grew out of NPPUG, who run monthly meetups all year round in Norwich.</p>
              <a href="https://www.nppug.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: var(--yellow); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px;">nppug.co.uk</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider" />
        <h3 class="h3" style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 12px;">Meet the team</h3>
        <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">EoES is organised entirely by volunteers who are passionate about the Microsoft community.</p>
        <a href="/about" style="color: var(--yellow); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase;">Meet the team →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-6">
        <article class="card" style="padding: 32px;">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">— Speakers 2027 —</div>
          <h3 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Want to speak?</h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Speaker submissions for EoES 2027 will open via Sessionize in late 2026. Follow us on LinkedIn to be the first to know when the call for speakers opens.</p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/eoes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn--primary">Follow on LinkedIn</a>
        </article>

        <article class="card" style="padding: 32px; border-color: rgba(251,191,36,0.3); background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.06) 0%, transparent 100%);">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">— Sponsorship —</div>
          <h3 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Sponsorship enquiries.</h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Five tiers from £250 to £6,000, an exclusive Recruitment Partner package, and five add-ons. Get the full prospectus.</p>
          <a href="/sponsorship" class="btn btn--ghost">View sponsorship options</a>
        </article>

        <article class="card" style="padding: 32px;">
          <div class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">— Volunteering —</div>
          <h3 class="h3" style="margin-bottom: 14px;">Want to volunteer?</h3>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">EoES is run by community volunteers. If you'd like to help on the day — registration, room hosting, social — drop us a line.</p>
          <a href="mailto:info@eoepps.co.uk?subject=Volunteer%20enquiry%20-%20EoES%202027" class="btn btn--ghost">Email us</a>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
